	<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-4264" >
		<div class="c-grav"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ebd3b90b30e78d29cc01c13ba6ebb090?s=40&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D40&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' /></div>
		<div class="c-body">
			<div class="c-head">
