	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-4323" >
		<div class="c-grav"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/395e1a89e98eb6e37170be1b4f349e4c?s=40&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D40&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' /></div>
		<div class="c-body">
