	<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-4518" >
		<div class="c-grav"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/8479d4e0524eabc8434f73dca4761b17?s=40&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D40&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' /></div>
		<div class="c-body">
			<div class="c-head">
